        <p>Welcome to FamPass. These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of the FamPass mobile application (the "App") operated by Appystrano, LLC ("we," "our," or "us"). By downloading, installing, or using the App, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the App.</p>

        <h2>1. Service Description</h2>
        <p>FamPass is a family event discovery application that helps parents and caregivers find family-friendly events and activities in select metropolitan areas across the United States.</p>
        <p>The App aggregates event information from various third-party sources and presents it in a curated, searchable format. Users can browse events, save favorites, and receive personalized recommendations based on their selected metro area.</p>

        <h2>2. Account Registration</h2>
